imdb.plot outline: This series showcases the extraordinary and often dangerous work of two of Australia's largest State Police Dog units as they help track and capture criminals. Each episode features exciting stories of how specially trained dogs track fugitives through difficult terrain and hunt for drugs, explosives, and weapons. We witness the incredible bond that develops between the dogs and their handlers.
imdb.title: Send in the Dogs Australia
plot: _Send in the Dogs Australia_ (qv) showcases the extraordinary and often dangerous work of two of Australia's largest State Police Dog units as they track down criminals, drugs, explosives, and weapons.
